waterelf details:

Colour code for 6 pin connector
Pin	Wire Colour			Function
1	Orange+Orange/White	VCC (5v)	Red
2	Green/White			Trig		Yellow
3	Blue/White			Echo		White
4	Brown+Brown/White	Gnd			Black
5	Green				Pump		Green
6	Blue				Solenoid	Blue

echo sensor HC-SR04

Colour code for Cat5 wire:

Pin	Wire colour			Function
1	Orange+Orange/White	VCC (5v)
2	Green+Green/White	Trig
3	Blue+Blue/White		Echo
4	Brown+Brown/White	Gnd

Temp sensor DS18B20

Colour code for 3 core wire / 3 pin connector:

Pin	Wire colour			Function
1	Black				Gnd
2	Red					VCC (3.3v)
3	Yellow				Signal

AM2302 Temp/Humidity Sensor
Pin	Wire Colour			Function
1	Orange+Orange/White	Vcc (3.3v)
2	Green+Green/White	Data
3	Blue+Blue/White		NC
4	Brown+Brown/White	Gnd

pins on header connector, looking from above, tab at top
pins on board, looking from sensor side, connections at bottom

esp8266 pins
0  air temp/humid
2  water temp
4  i2c SDA
5  i2c SCL
12 water level transmit
13 water level echo1
14 water level echo2
15 433 transmit
16 water level echo3

mcp pins
0 - pump 1
1 - solenoid 3
2 - solenoid 1
3 - pump 2
6 - solenoid 2
7 - pump 3
